http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Lit.label: Literal
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Lit.definition: The class of literal values, eg. textual strings and integers.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Con.label: ContainerMembershipProperty
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Con.definition:
The class of container membership properties, rdf:_1, rdf:_2, ...,
                    all of which are sub-properties of 'member'.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isD.label: isDefinedBy
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isD.definition: The defininition of the subject resource.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.label: label
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.definition: A human-readable name for the subject.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.label: comment
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.definition: A description of the subject resource.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#sub.label: subClassOf
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#sub.definition: The subject is a subclass of a class.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#ran.label: range
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#ran.definition: A range of the subject property.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#dom.label: domain
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#dom.definition: A domain of the subject property.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#sub.label: subPropertyOf
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#sub.definition: The subject is a subproperty of a property.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#see.label: seeAlso
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#see.definition: Further information about the subject resource.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#mem.label: member
http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#mem.definition: A member of the subject resource.
